[Signal](https://signal.org/) is a secure messaging platform. 

For DWebYVR, we use Signal for asynchronous messaging to plan events, compare notes on DWeb developments, and for general merriment. 

Join the groupchat [here](https://signal.group/#CjQKIODy2EEMBP_tF0YP4t3-WzGRqaHCDChDnldfEl8A29OmEhAuVXCHCC91O7p2OIdqE5OC)
